        "created_at": "2022-01-19T05:27:17.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>My first encounter with this new Domaine.</p>\n<p>Bright and sappy red fruits with a cherry cola-lite character, soft florals, and tilled earth. The texture is supremely silky and generous, seductive, with a slight frame of structure and lively acidity. Lightly smoky and spicy finish. I\u2019m unsure of whether this is a long-term hold but it\u2019s plenty charming for the present.</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 5,
        "updated_at": "2022-06-04T11:44:19.676Z",
